<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: G. F.</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-10 20:17:14</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>First of all, yes, this robe does in fact exist. It is looted from Cazic Thule, a god found in the Plane of Fear. He's one of, if not the, toughest enemies currently in EverQuest. There are 2 or 3 people on my server, Prexus, who have this robe. There is a SS of Dryfter Shortleg in some of the past news at the KoF website (http://www.gamelanusa.com/keepers/) with this robe on. She's a level 50 wizard, so it's not a RoE she's wearing, which looks exactly the same as CRoA. I hate it when people post stuff and they have no idea what they're talking about. Get the facts before you know-it-alls post false information.</font></td></tr></table>
